Doctor Strange is voiced by Liam O'Brien, who has been voicing the character in different Marvel projects since 2013. Liam is best known for being one of the cast members and player of the web series Critical Role , as well numerous roles in video games, animes and cartoons, most notably Illidan Stormrage in World of Warcraft and Gaara in Naruto and its sequels .
